{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呼，终于解决了。这样一来，\\n这一带的村子应该太平了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "最近魔兽越发凶暴了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。不少家伙棘手到\\n不龙化就无法打倒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "龙化吗。尤蒂尔，\\n可以问你点事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "什么事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "佩罗和奇罗现在还是孩子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "但他们很快就会成长为像他们父亲那样\\n拥有强大力量的龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "到了那时，\\n你会和他们缔结契约吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这个我还没想过。\\n至少目前没有……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "目前？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也许今后会遇到\\n更强大的敌人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "到那时，我就会需要\\n更多龙的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "如果能得到佩罗和奇罗的帮助，\\n我心里会更有底。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过是否缔结契约，\\n取决于他们自己的意愿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是特训吗？\\n扎因弗拉德。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "是啊，尤蒂尔。\\n如你所见。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "至今还没见过你特训呢，\\n今天是怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "你还记得我说过，\\n我们一族曾在与敌对部族的\\n斗争中败下阵来吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。而且你们一族崇拜的龙……\\n佩罗他们的父亲也死了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "敌对部族\\n对我们的村子进行了突袭。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "当时，他们的父亲\\n为了保护我们族人舍身战斗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "他们的父亲秉持着“为他人而战”\\n的强大信念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "而佩罗他们\\n继承了他的意志。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "从盗贼手上保护我们的时候，\\n他们的眼神和父亲非常相似。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "佩罗和奇罗也会\\n为了他人而战？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "是啊。所以我下定决心\\n“当佩罗他们长大后，\\n我要守护他们战斗的身影”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "为此，我要变得比现在更强。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "那便是身为“龙之守护者”的、\\n我的使命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊。\\n如果有什么我能做的，我都愿意帮忙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n如果你需要龙的力量，\\n我希望你和他们缔结契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "如果是为众人而战的你，\\n他们一定也愿意。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "届时身为他们主人的你，\\n也由我来保护。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢你，扎因弗拉德。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过，\\n影响了佩罗他们的，\\n不只是他们的父亲吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "孩子是看着父亲的背影长大的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我想他们一定也对战斗着的\\n扎因弗拉德心怀憧憬。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "扎因弗拉德",
            "context": "是……这样吗？\\n如果是这样，还真有点感动呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110021_01_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}